# ── Root-level binary guard (F-252) ──────────────────────────
# Prevent accidental commit of binary snapshots at repo root.
# The_One_and_Only_Master_Build_v_30.xlsx is the sole exception.
/*.zip
/*.xlsx
/*.docx
/*.pdf
!/The_One_and_Only_Master_Build_v_30.xlsx
